These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: rock, pop, hip-hop, country, indie, r&b, funk
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of indie is between the fan of rock and the fan of hip-hop##2
5. the fan of country is between the fan of pop and the fan of rock##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | hip-hop | indie | rock | country | pop | r&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, hiking, board-games, magic-tricks, dancing, puzzles, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | traveling | reading | board-games | magic-tricks | hiking | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
