3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | camping | filmmaking | magic-tricks | drawing | collecting | video-games |

