5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | card-games | skydiving | collecting | baking | photography | traveling | board-games |

