3. the person watching crime movies is the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching superhero movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | crime | thriller | horror | adventure | superhero | documentary |

