2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
4. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the ferret##2
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1  |     2      |  3  |  4   |    5     |   6   |  7   |
